extraction.query:
SELECT *
FROM
  STATUS_VALUE sv,
  STATUS_TYPE st
WHERE
  sv.STATUS_TYPE_GID = st.STATUS_TYPE_GID
  AND st.IS_EXTERNAL = 'Y'
  AND (
    EXISTS (
      SELECT 1
      FROM SHIPMENT_STATUS ss
      WHERE ss.STATUS_TYPE_GID = st.STATUS_TYPE_GID
        AND ss.UPDATE_DATE >= TO_DATE('02/01/2026','DD/MM/YYYY')
    )
    OR EXISTS (
      SELECT 1
      FROM ORDER_RELEASE_STATUS ors
      WHERE ors.STATUS_TYPE_GID = st.STATUS_TYPE_GID
        AND ors.UPDATE_DATE >= TO_DATE('02/01/2026','DD/MM/YYYY')
    )
  )
ORDER BY
  st.DOMAIN_NAME,
  st.OBJECT_TYPE,
  st.STATUS_TYPE_GID,
  sv.SEQUENCE

SELECT *
FROM
  STATUS_VALUE sv,
  STATUS_TYPE st
WHERE
  sv.STATUS_TYPE_GID = st.STATUS_TYPE_GID
  AND st.IS_EXTERNAL = 'Y'
  AND (
    EXISTS (
      SELECT 1
      FROM SHIPMENT_STATUS ss
      WHERE ss.STATUS_TYPE_GID = st.STATUS_TYPE_GID
        AND ss.UPDATE_DATE >= TO_DATE('02/01/2026','DD/MM/YYYY')
    )
    OR EXISTS (
      SELECT 1
      FROM ORDER_RELEASE_STATUS ors
      WHERE ors.STATUS_TYPE_GID = st.STATUS_TYPE_GID
        AND ors.UPDATE_DATE >= TO_DATE('02/01/2026','DD/MM/YYYY')
    )
  )
ORDER BY
  st.DOMAIN_NAME,
  st.OBJECT_TYPE,
  st.STATUS_TYPE_GID,
  sv.SEQUENCE
